utions. Under perturbed\ndistributions, the Rao's $\\beta$-score tests outperform any classical test.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2020 14:12:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jan 2021 04:30:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-05"}
